<section class="install-section">
<div class="container">
	<div class="install-grid">
		<div class="install-left">
			<h2>Get started<br />in <span class="hl">seconds</span>.</h2>
			<p>Four packages. One ecosystem. Parse and validate skills with the core library, lint them with the CLI, route by intent with embeddings, or generate from your existing API specs.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="terminal">
			<div class="terminal-bar">
				<span class="tdot tdot-r"></span><span class="tdot tdot-y"></span><span class="tdot tdot-g"></span>
				<span class="tfile">~/project</span>
			</div>
			<pre><code><span class="t-p">$</span> npm i @skill-tools/core       <span class="t-c"># parser &amp; types</span>
<span class="t-p">$</span> npm i -g skill-tools           <span class="t-c"># validate, lint, score</span>
<span class="t-p">$</span> npm i skillrouter           <span class="t-c"># semantic routing</span>
<span class="t-p">$</span> npm i -g skillgen           <span class="t-c"># generate from OpenAPI</span></code></pre>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</section>

<style>
	.install-section {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 10;
		padding: 6rem 0;
	}

	.install-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.install-left h2 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		line-height: 1.05;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	.install-left .hl {
		color: var(--green);
	}

	.install-left p {
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		max-width: 440px;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.install-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.install-section {
			padding: 4rem 0;
		}
	}
</style>
